The paper discusses the challenges of publishing dynamic data on the web in a scalable manner, which is a common problem in the field of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also proposes the use of context-dependent publication heuristics, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.DL) techniques. The use of Schema.org for structured data is also mentioned, which is a topic in web science (cs.WEB) and semantic web (cs.SI).
